  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Completion of a qualifying Ra Pharmaceuticals sponsored RA101495 PNH study

          -  Evidence of ongoing clinical benefit in the opinion of the Investigator

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  History of meningococcal disease

          -  Current systemic infection or suspicion of active bacterial infection
      </textblock>
